<h1 style="font-size:20px; line-height:22px; height:22px; margin-bottom:10px;">驺虞</h1>
<p class="source"><a href="https://www.gushiwen.org/shiwen/default.aspx?cstr=%e5%85%88%e7%a7%a6">先秦</a><span>：</span><a href="/search.aspx?value=%e4%bd%9a%e5%90%8d">佚名</a> </p>
<div class="contson" id="contsonc9e195985a2c">
彼茁者葭，壹发五豝，于嗟乎驺虞！<br />彼茁者蓬，壹发五豵，于嗟乎驺虞！
</div>
</div>
<div class="tool">
<div class="shoucang"><iframe style="width:18px; height:30px; border:0px;" src="/shiwen2017/like.aspx?idsw=25&from=http://so.gushiwen.org/shiwenv.aspx?id=c9e195985a2c"></iframe></div>
